<h3 class="text">VIP Airport Pick Up</h3>
<p class="text"><strong>(Gregorio   Luperon International Airport) POP:</strong> One Way US$ 65.00.</p>
<ul>
  <li class="text">BE   CAREFUL:Payment must be done at RCL office not to taxi driver. </li>
  <li class="text">Each   Airport transfer has a Maximum of 6 people + Luggage per vehicle. </li>
  <li class="text">Customer   must specify: landing time, airport, airline, date, at the moment that requests   Airport VIP Pick Up Service. </li>
</ul>
<ol>
  <li class="text">If   you need this service it must be ordered at the moment of your villas'   reservation. </li>
  <li class="text">On   arrival staff at the airport are waiting for you and will take you to a VIP   section (air conditioned room - no smoking). </li>
  <li class="text">They   make the registration very quickly, luggage transportation is included, after   they finish they take the customer to the assigned transportation outside   (taxi). </li>
  <li class="text">Tourist   card is NOT INCLUDDED, clients must pay for that. </li>
  <li class="text">If   required for departures: clients must make a line (normal check in) after that   can comfortably await for the flight in the VIP area. (Reservation must be done   1 day prior). </li>
</ol>
